<section class="overview fade-in">
  <h2>Project Overview: Lunar Terrain Reconstruction and Visualization System</h2>
  <p>
    Internally referred to as <strong>ISRO HAVK</strong>, this solution transforms a single 2D image of the lunar surface
    into an interactive, data-rich 3D terrain model. It provides topographical insights and analysis tools for mission
    planners, engineers, and astronauts to improve safety and operational efficiency during lunar missions.
  </p>
</section>

